NON-TECH
	GenSailingShip Command-Tendering. Enables
	transfer between two sailing ships of goods and services. Tendering may be
	accomplished via small boats or via direct ship-to-ship boarding. Either way,
	the affect is that the crew and can transfer from one ship to another ship
	When a ship TENDERs to a target ship, both ship's gangplanks are extended to
	the other ship, creating a permanent connection which is instantly broken if
	either ship leaves the room or enters combat.'
